title: IFaxDoc::get_SenderOfficePhone (faxcom.h)
description: Sets or retrieves the SenderOfficePhone property of a FaxDoc object. The SenderOfficePhone property is a null-terminated string that contains the office telephone number of the sender of the fax transmission. (Get)
